{"tid":2227657,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黃國健︰民主派留任默認中央權力 胡志偉︰部署更謹慎","createTime":"2020-10-03T03:29:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T03:51:45.000Z","uid":156254,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b8a463d3369ff0f02b5ac0f4845327dc3bfbb8c5","tid":2227657,"uid":156254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T03:29:32.000Z","msg":"黃國健︰民主派留任默認中央權力 胡志偉︰部署更謹慎<br />\n2020-10-03 HKT 10:17<br />\n 分享工具 facebook twitter<br />\n黃國健（左）認為民主派留任有助立法會獲認受。胡志偉（右）說，留任議員更加要做好本身工作。<br />\n黃國健（左）認為民主派留任有助立法會獲認受。胡志偉（右）說，留任議員更加要做好本身工作。<br />\n工聯會立法會議員黃國健認為，留任立法會的民主派議員，已經默認中央對本港的權力，亦應該利用今次契機，緩和與中央及特區政府的關係。<br />\n<br />\n黃國健出席一個電台節目時說，個人支持民主派留任，認為有助立法會獲認受，避免美國及其他西方國家指責立法會缺乏認受，而有藉口干預。<br />\n<br />\n新任民主派會議召集人胡志偉就說，明白留任議員一定被外界用放大鏡審視表現，要求更高，因此留任議員更加要做好本身工作，部署亦會較以往小心謹慎。他希望可拖慢政府有關容許選民於粵港澳大灣區投票，以及「明日大嶼」撥款的進展。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1552858-20201003.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1552858-20201003.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmTRqNRg6ChYs1Sy50pDDGUM%3D&h=adfb493f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1552858-20201003.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7c4068de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1552858-20201003.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n泛民比689, 工聯會入晒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68babed2a64066fbcd65aae51b9820d97112cdd9","tid":2227657,"uid":54431,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T03:35:10.000Z","msg":"胡志偉都唔敢回應隻建制狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p